name: Songs In the Key of Tweed
description:
The debut album from A&TKH, featuring all of your favourite hits from the band such as "Fart in the Car", "If it Moves..." and "Pregnant Ladies (Put Your Thing In It)".

Fuelled with Scones, Tea, Ale and Italian cuisine, A&TKH crafted this album at the Call Exchange Studios, Yorkshire.

Track listing:

1. "If it Moves"
2. "Pregnant Ladies (Put Your Thing In It)"
3. "A Tub of Margarine"
4. "Randy"
5. "Strangeways Prison Blues"
6. "I Wan'na Be Like You (A Monkey Song)"
7. "Fart in the Car"
8. "I Like a Good Bratty"
9. "You and I"
